Covid-19 vaccines not linked to Sudden Arrhythmic Death Syndromes Social media posts claim "Sudden Adult Death Syndrome" is a new condition linked to the Covid-19 vaccine, proving that Sudden Infant Death Syndrome (SIDS) is also a vaccine side effect.
